[{"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T21:25:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/29fd869adf2940032cb40abbf8e428d4.jpg\" /><p>Some games make my heart bubble up with joy. They remind me of thumbing through tiny, beautiful booklets and tag-teaming tough bosses with friends. Not everyone\u2019s childhood was easy, simple, or happy, but all of us have moments in our lives we look back  fondly on and games that briefly bring them back to us. <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/panzer-paladin-is-the-retro-throwback-i-needed-this-sum-1844457070\">Panzer\u2026</a></p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/panzer-paladin-ps5-trophies-zelda-2-mega-man-retro-8bit-1851554364\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 755737, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/panzer-paladin-ps5-trophies-zelda-2-mega-man-retro-8bit-1851554364", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/29fd869adf2940032cb40abbf8e428d4.jpg", "title": "An Underrated Mashup Of Zelda 2 And Mega Man Is Finally Getting The Multiplatform Love It Deserves", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T20:40:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/d90b00f8522195bc11ab38c4975f57d8.jpg\" /><p>So, you made it to the top of the tower in Belurat. Give yourself a pat on the back, that\u2019s no easy task by itself. Those jerks with the giant maces ain\u2019t messing around. Unfortunately, you\u2019ve got one last challenge to take on before making your leave of the place, and if you\u2019re having trouble getting through the\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/shadow-erdtree-dancing-lion-divine-beast-boss-tips-1851554371\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 755371, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/shadow-erdtree-dancing-lion-divine-beast-boss-tips-1851554371", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/d90b00f8522195bc11ab38c4975f57d8.jpg", "title": "How To Defeat Divine Beast Dancing Lion In Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T20:30:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/c95843f397f341bf1ed77463b2491ef2.jpg\" /><p>The Spirit Ash for Curseblade Meera summons the titular spirit to help you do battle, but it can only be found in <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/games/elden-ring\">Elden Ring</a>\u2019s <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-dlc-expansion-review-1851545505\">Shadow of the Erdtree</a> expansion. If you\u2019d like to add this Spirit Ash to your collection, you\u2019ll need to tackle a perilous dungeon and defeat a tough boss.<br /></p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-curseblade-meera-spirit-ash-where-find-1851554428\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 755372, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-curseblade-meera-spirit-ash-where-find-1851554428", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/c95843f397f341bf1ed77463b2491ef2.jpg", "title": "Where To Find Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree's Curseblade Meera Spirit Ash", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T19:49:12+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/74e51a6b3a70030a50dcc9ae0ab95cdf.jpg\" /><p>The Star-Lined Sword is a Katana that can be found in <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/games/elden-ring\">Elden Ring</a>\u2019s <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-dlc-expansion-review-1851545505\">Shadow of the Erdtree</a> expansion. It\u2019s an excellent option for DEX/INT builds and features a cool move set that keeps things interesting in combat, especially if you make good use of its unique Ash of War. If you like to wield katanas and look flashy\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-star-lined-sword-where-find-1851554306\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 755373, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-star-lined-sword-where-find-1851554306", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/74e51a6b3a70030a50dcc9ae0ab95cdf.jpg", "title": "Where To Find Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree's Star-Lined Sword", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T19:37:50+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f1f57f867c5e55e0efd679b5f437a578.jpg\" /><p>The Smithscript Dagger is a Throwing Weapon found in <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/games/elden-ring\">Elden Ring</a>\u2019s <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-dlc-expansion-review-1851545505\">Shadow of the Erdtree</a> expansion. This new weapon type allows you to throw daggers to deal ranged damage to foes, so you should definitely add the Smithscript Dagger to your collection if you want to keep your enemies at a distance.<br /></p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-smithscript-dagger-1851554281\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 755017, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-smithscript-dagger-1851554281", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f1f57f867c5e55e0efd679b5f437a578.jpg", "title": "Where To Find Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree's Smithscript Dagger", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T19:27:06+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/2d14de1118fce93ef489ab58eea8a02b.jpg\" /><p>The Anvil Hammer is a Colossal Weapon found in Elden Ring\u2019s Shadow of the Erdtree expansion. It can deal some very hefty damage to your enemies while also breaking their stance easily, making this a top-notch choice for Strength builds seeking some extra power. If that sounds up your alley, you won\u2019t want to miss this\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/anvil-hammer-elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-where-find-1851554248\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 755018, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/anvil-hammer-elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-where-find-1851554248", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/2d14de1118fce93ef489ab58eea8a02b.jpg", "title": "Where To Find Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree's Anvil Hammer", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T19:15:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6b966d6037dd24577993f78a9ef28130.jpg\" /><p>Milady is a Light Greatsword found in Elden Ring\u2019s Shadow of the Erdtree expansion. It bridges the gap between a straight sword and a greatsword, giving you faster attacks that still deal plenty of damage. It also provides a fun and visually intriguing move set that makes it a joy to use in combat.</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/where-to-find-elden-ring-shadows-of-the-erdtrees-milad-1851554210\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 755019, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/where-to-find-elden-ring-shadows-of-the-erdtrees-milad-1851554210", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6b966d6037dd24577993f78a9ef28130.jpg", "title": "Where To Find Elden Ring: Shadows Of The Erdtree's Milady", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T19:02:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/3aec416fd8648b624a11e0338ee81ad9.jpg\" /><p>Our Midgar-raised, spellcasting Flower Girl is pretty handy at this whole magic business. Equipped with the right staff, Aerith can not only ascend to cause dramatic devastation for your enemies, but she can also keep your party healthy via her limit breaks and very high magic stats. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-7-ff7-rebirth-aerith-best-staff-1851554138\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 755020, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-7-ff7-rebirth-aerith-best-staff-1851554138", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/3aec416fd8648b624a11e0338ee81ad9.jpg", "title": "Final Fantasy VII Rebirth\u2019s Best Weapons For Aerith", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T18:35:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/950da40456b0e895da664757c04155a8.jpg\" /><p><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/kingdom-hearts-best-games-ranked-2-3-birth-by-sleep-1851494518\">Kingdom Hearts</a> fans waited nearly 20 years for Sora, Donald, and Goofy\u2019s adventures through Disney worlds to come to PC, which they finally did back in 2021 via the Epic Games Store. But some fans waited even longer for most of the series to <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/kingdom-hearts-steam-release-date-bundle-deck-1851490495\">come to Steam on June 13</a>. Whatever floats your steamboat, PC players. Use\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/kingdom-hearts-steam-user-reviews-epic-games-store-1851554071\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 754702, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/kingdom-hearts-steam-user-reviews-epic-games-store-1851554071", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/950da40456b0e895da664757c04155a8.jpg", "title": "Kingdom Hearts, As Told By Steam Reviews", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T18:25:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/7f26a7f1976852455f2f45beefd02f0c.jpg\" /><p>The Black Steel Greathammer is a Greathammer found exclusively in Elden Ring\u2019s Shadow of the Erdtree expansion. This big and powerful hammer can make short work of foes that stand in your way\u2014so long as you have the appropriate stats to wield it. This is a weapon designed for a Strength/Faith hybrid build, so if that\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-black-steel-greathammer-where-find-1851554063\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 754703, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-black-steel-greathammer-where-find-1851554063", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/7f26a7f1976852455f2f45beefd02f0c.jpg", "title": "Where To Find Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree's Black Steel Greathammer", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T18:10:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/8b84fe07d14422cff0af4a45c90cdd79.jpg\" /><p><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/helldivers-2-kotaku-review-pc-ps5-is-it-good-ps-plus-1851258251\">Helldivers 2</a> has always featured multiple different kinds of planets and biomes, but it\u2019s finally added an entirely new one alongside its Viper Commandos warbond that\u2019s been a hit with fans. It is, of course, a <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/Helldivers/comments/1dkf19g/the_new_planet_biome_is_sick/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">jungle</a>, perfect for everyone trying to relive their deepest Rambo or Predator fantasies.</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/helldivers-2-jungle-biome-reactions-1851553947\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 754704, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/helldivers-2-jungle-biome-reactions-1851553947", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/8b84fe07d14422cff0af4a45c90cdd79.jpg", "title": "Fans Are In Love With Helldivers 2's New Jungle Planet", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T17:55:00+00:00", "description": "<video loop=\"\" poster=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/73832f284b5af