ve success for Riot, and fans are already hoping for more adaptations in the aftermath of Arcane\u2019s end. The rest of Runeterra (the Le\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/riot-games-arcane-valorant-netflix-series-1851553868\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 754253, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/riot-games-arcane-valorant-netflix-series-1851553868", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/3f03d88d00544e02d3660ee22b01c62f.jpg", "title": "With Arcane Ending, Valorant Deserves The Adaptation Treatment", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T17:08:17+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6d4fa2ec302c99eddce8bf8aa1f806b5.jpg\" /><p>Every <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/overwatch-2-skins-characters-reddit-steam-2023-1851119014\">Overwatch 2</a> player has opinions about balance changes and reworks for their favorite heroes. Sometimes they\u2019re impractical power fantasies to make their main more powerful, but other times, there are some real thoughtful ideas floating around forums and social media. Blizzard gave a handful of creators a chance\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/overwatch-2-community-crafted-eskay-brigitte-inspire-1851553786\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 754254, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/overwatch-2-community-crafted-eskay-brigitte-inspire-1851553786", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6d4fa2ec302c99eddce8bf8aa1f806b5.jpg", "title": "Community-Made Overwatch 2 Mode Is So Good Fans Want Some Of Its Changes In The Main Game", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T16:55:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/af162f3c90bf7712c0fdd2e060ac949c.jpg\" /><p>The Beast Claw is a Fist weapon found in Elden Ring\u2019s Shadow of the Erdtree expansion. This fast and deadly weapon has one of the coolest movesets in the game, and it\u2019s readily available within the first few minutes of arriving in the Land of Shadow. As such, this is one you\u2019ll want to grab right away if you\u2019re\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-beast-claw-guide-1851553737\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 754255, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-beast-claw-guide-1851553737", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/af162f3c90bf7712c0fdd2e060ac949c.jpg", "title": "Where To Find Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree's Beast Claw", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T16:46:57+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/469a3e61c42e8d3d9520b029e7ddfe52.jpg\" /><p>Sometimes all it takes to grab my attention is one trailer. One good teaser. And that\u2019s exactly how I discovered Blud, a newly released 2D Zelda-like action game about vampires, evil tech bros, and high school. I saw its release trailer on Twitter, thought \u201cWow that looks cool!\u201d and started playing it. The game, with\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/blud-90s-cartoon-animated-zelda-vampire-cartoon-rpg-1851553695\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 754256, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/blud-90s-cartoon-animated-zelda-vampire-cartoon-rpg-1851553695", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/469a3e61c42e8d3d9520b029e7ddfe52.jpg", "title": "New Zelda-Like Is A Fun '90s Cartoon Take On Killing Vampires", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T16:30:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b98c63c0295c277c3671d75e4a2c1a15.jpg\" /><p>Vehicles aren\u2019t just in Fortnite\u2019s battle royale. They\u2019re also every minifig\u2019s favorite way to get around in the Lego version of Epic\u2019s hit game, especially if you decide to have a base in each of the biomes so you can grab materials from each different environment. In order to have working vehicles though, you\u2019ll\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/lego-fortnite-how-to-craft-power-cells-cars-1851553634\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 753693, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/lego-fortnite-how-to-craft-power-cells-cars-1851553634", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b98c63c0295c277c3671d75e4a2c1a15.jpg", "title": "How To Craft Power Cells In Lego Fortnite", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T16:15:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/0e3ed04c661b67557840b33dda78b9d2.jpg\" /><p>The Backhand Blade is a (you guessed it!) Backhand Blade weapon found in Elden Ring\u2019s Shadow of the Erdtree expansion. This weapon can be one-handed or two-handed and offers you an agile playstyle that lets you aggressively punish your foes. If you\u2019re looking to get in and get out regularly, you\u2019ll find the Backhand\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/backhand-blade-elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-where-guide-1851553583\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 753694, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/backhand-blade-elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-where-guide-1851553583", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/0e3ed04c661b67557840b33dda78b9d2.jpg", "title": "Where To Find Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree's Backhand Blade", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T16:07:24+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/4a8b3e9a262e52e9026cc082b2200b28.jpg\" /><p>The Great Katana is, well, a Great Katana found in Elden Ring\u2019s Shadow of the Erdtree expansion. This heavy weapon is a powerful option for those who enjoy using katanas but want to be able to stance-break more efficiently and dish out more damage at the same time. You know what the say: Go big or go home, right?\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-where-to-find-the-gr-1851553558\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 753695, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-where-to-find-the-gr-1851553558", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/4a8b3e9a262e52e9026cc082b2200b28.jpg", "title": "Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree: Where To Find The Great Katana", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T15:52:31+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f1ad9bba03f327df96299dc74bec788e.jpg\" /><p>With a full-blown Astro Bot platformer on the way, Sony\u2019s Team Asobi has revisited its PS5 launch game, Astro\u2019s Playroom, to add some exciting new teases for what\u2019s to come. Most notable are the addition of four new Special Bots hidden in each of the game\u2019s core worlds. If you\u2019re looking to round up the Bloodborne\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/astros-playroom-special-bot-gpu-jungle-bloodborne-1851553463\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 753696, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/astros-playroom-special-bot-gpu-jungle-bloodborne-1851553463", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f1ad9bba03f327df96299dc74bec788e.jpg", "title": "Astro's Playroom: How To Find The New Bloodborne Special Bot In GPU Jungle", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T15:25:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/a7aa77b6a2d30de18f7f51caf4496fbe.jpg\" /><p><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-dlc-expansion-review-1851545505\">Shadow of the Erdtree</a> is already bringing <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/games/elden-ring\">Elden Ring</a> players together before they\u2019ve even accessed the expansion\u2019s content. As a requirement to get into the DLC area, <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-dlc-mogh-achievement-1851531884\">you must have defeated</a> Starscourge Radhan and Lord Mohg, and generous folks are currently posting up outside of the latter\u2019s arena to offer help in\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-help-mohg-1851553244\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 753285, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-help-mohg-1851553244", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/a7aa77b6a2d30de18f7f51caf4496fbe.jpg", "title": "No Elden Ring Player Left Behind As They Help Each Other Beat DLC-Blocking Boss", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T15:10:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/28c9c03978a313c53531673947fc6203.jpg\" /><p>In the first episode of <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/x-men-97-disney-plus-premiere-impressions-1851356830\">X-Men \u201897</a>, the sequel to the classic X-Men: Animated Series cartoon, the titular mutant team finds themselves falling through the sky after their plane gets blown up. To stop his descent, team leader <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/games/x-men-character-cyclops\">Cyclops</a> emits a massive concussive blast from his eyes, slowing his fall and creating a massive\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/x-men-97-cyclops-scott-summers-redemption-1851553243\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 753286, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/x-men-97-cyclops-scott-summers-redemption-1851553243", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/28c9c03978a313c53531673947fc6203.jpg", "title": "X-Men \u201897 Didn\u2019t Redeem Cyclops, He\u2019s Always Been This Cool", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T15:00:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/97a73d3103dba138e8a80f84a87818c1.jpg\" /><p>It is now officially summer. Yesterday, the solstice (Litha, as it\u2019s known to some) brought us our longest day of the calendar year, and now we march on to ever darkening days. But right now, we\u2019re just marching on into the weekend to spend that time off in some delightful digital realms. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/kotaku-games-to-play-dragon-age-nine-sols-starfield-1851553216\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 753287, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/kotaku-games-to-play-dragon-age-nine-sols-starfield-1851553216", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/97a73d3103dba138e8a80f84a87818c1.jpg", "title": "Kotaku\u2019s Weekend Guide: Six Amazing Games We Refuse To Stop Playing", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T14:51:35+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/2584faf1f1fe74d3ca842396f904938c.jpg\" /><p>Real talk: there\u2019s nothing that truly prepares you for jumping into a Souls game. But even FromSoftware knows a fair warning about what\u2019s coming can go a hell of a long way. So, take it from one who has traversed the Realm of Shadow and (sorta) lived to tell the tale, there\u2019s a few things I can tell those who will be\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-beginner-tips-guide-1851553242\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 753288, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-beginner-tips-guide-1851553242", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/2584faf1f1fe74d3ca842396f904938c.jpg", "title": "9 Things I Wish I Knew Before Starting Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T14:35:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/e7d428b5f08d4afe2fdb4a856fbebdfa.jpg\" /><p>To a lot of people, Reinhardt is still the quintessential tank character in <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/overwatch-2-anniversary-reddit-review-competitive-rank-1850896550\">Overwatch 2</a>. The shield-bearing, hammer-swinging old man is one of the original 21 heroes, has some of the most straightforward and comprehensible utility of any character on the roster, and he\u2019s overall just a fun character to have in your\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/overwatch-2-season-11-patch-notes-reinhardt-kiriko-1851553176\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 753289, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/overwatch-2-season-11-patch-notes-reinhardt-kiriko-1851553176", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/e7d428b5f08d4afe2fdb4a856fbebdfa.jpg", "title": "Reinhardt Mains Just Got Their First Overwatch 2 Win In A Hot Minute", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T14:25:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f376deb341e395b8f9937dff8692c378.jpg\" /><p>It\u2019s Elden Ring day, again. Shadow of the Erdtree, its long-awaited and massive expansion, is finally live and, surprise, it\u2019s really, really hard. Even veteran players are getting their asses kicked. Whether it\u2019s new bosses or random scrubs out in the field, everything seems to be hitting harder and Elden Ring sickos\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-difficulty-vigor-dying-1851553144\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 753290, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/elden-ring-shadow-erdtree-difficulty-vigor-dying-1851553144", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f376deb341e395b8f9937dff8692c378.jpg", "title": "Veteran Elden Ring Players Can't Believe How Much The DLC Is Kicking Their Asses", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-06-21T13:55:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/7bb756a71eb2f94562fda41a34aee289.jpg\" /><p>There\u2019s a place called prison and a place called gaol....<br /></p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/shadow-of-the-erdtree-blackgaol-knight-guide-1851553065\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 752728, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/shadow-of-the-erdtree-blackgaol-knight-guide-1851553065", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "source_obj__id": 175, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/7bb756a71eb2f94562fda41a34aee289.jpg", "title": "How To Defeat The Blackgaol Knight In Elden Ring: Shadow of the Erdtree", "user": null, "vote": 0}]